724464f-a.title: Manhattan: West End Avenue - 90th Street (West)
724464f-a.text:
620-638 West End Avenue, from 90th to Glst Streets, a block of residences built between 1891 and 1897, except the twin houses at either end of the block, which were erected a few years later,
probably about 1900.
June 1925.
